[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0599","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0599.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0365","title":"Metamail mailcap 条目未过滤 shell 元字符远程命令执行漏洞","description":"metamail 邮件处理工具包中存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞，在将邮件内容传递给 mailcap 条目处理时未对 shell 元字符进行正确引号转义，导致远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制邮件触发命令执行。攻击者利用该漏洞可在受害者系统上以当前用户权限执行任意命令，影响广泛部署 metamail 的 Unix/Linux 系统。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0365"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.403","remediation":"升级 metamail 至 2.7-9 或更高版本，该版本已对 mailcap 文件中的 shell 元字符进行正确转义处理。如无法升级，可临时移除或禁用系统中所有不可信来源的 mailcap 配置项，同时限制邮件客户端自动调用 metamail 处理附件。在 sendmail 环境下，建议禁用自动执行 mailcap 条目的功能，并审查 /etc/mailcap 及用户 ~/.mailcap 中的每条规则，确保不含未引用的 shell 元字符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0365","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0365","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0365.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gmgp-r787-3hjp/GHSA-gmgp-r787-3hjp.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000513.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0365.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0599.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0594","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0594.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0362","title":"Ipswitch WS_FTP Server 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ipswitch WS_FTP Server 1.0.1 及 1.0.2 版本存在远程拒绝服务漏洞。未经身份认证的攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的 CWD（Change Working Directory）命令，导致 FTP 服务进程异常崩溃或停止响应，从而中断正常的文件传输服务。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危，受影响用户应升级至更高版本以修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0362"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.990","remediation":"升级至 WS_FTP Server 1.0.3 及以上版本可修复此漏洞；在防火墙中限制 FTP 服务端口的访问来源 IP，防止未授权远程连接发起 CWD 命令攻击。鉴于该产品版本过于老旧，建议迁移至受支持的最新版 WS_FTP Server 或替代 FTP 服务软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD02021999.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/217","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0362","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0362.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/wsftp_cwd_dos.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/Ipswitch%20WS_FTP%20Server%20prior%205.0.2%20CWD%20path%20denial%20of%20service.plugin","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0594.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0595","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0595.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0363","title":"S.u.S.E. Linux 5.2 lpc 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SuSE Linux 5.2 系统中的 lpc（行式打印机控制）程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 lpc 程序发送特制的输入参数触发该溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SuSE Linux 5.2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。由于需要本地访问权限，攻击者须先拥有系统普通用户账户方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0363"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.117","remediation":"升级 SuSE Linux 至 5.3 及以上版本，该版本已修复 lpc 程序缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，建议限制 lpc 可执行文件的 SUID 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/lpc）以降低提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/328","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19259","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0363.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0363","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0363.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0363.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79mx-82jw-xwqh/GHSA-79mx-82jw-xwqh.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0363.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/stucco/auto-labeled-corpus/blob/26e1e3a56dbcc0f6c9c39831bd7b9dcfec6c5f2f/src/python/preprocessing/autotag/exploitdb/bugtraq_cve_correspondence.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0595.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0595.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0595.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0619","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0619.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0383","title":"ACC Tigris 未授权访问漏洞","description":"ACC Tigris 系统存在未授权访问漏洞，远程攻击者无需任何身份认证凭据即可直接访问系统管理界面及敏感功能，获取完全控制权限。该漏洞影响 ACC Tigris 全线产品，攻击复杂度低，无需特殊权限或用户交互，危害等级高危（CVSS 7.5）。建议升级至支持认证机制的版本或通过访问控制策略限制来源 IP。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0383"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.773","remediation":"立即在所有 ACC Tigris 部署前添加反向代理认证（如 Nginx/Apache 的 Basic Auth 或 OAuth），并在防火墙层面将管理端口限制为仅可信 IP 段访问。由于该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的应用系统。如无法升级，至少配置 .htaccess 密码保护或 Web 服务器级别的访问控制列表。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/267","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/183"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0619.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0485","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0485.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0291","title":"Qbik WinGate 代理默认无密码未授权访问漏洞","description":"WinGate 代理服务器在默认安装时未设置访问密码，导致缺乏必要的身份认证机制。远程攻击者可在无需任何认证的条件下连接至该代理服务，利用其开放的代理功能转发网络连接请求，从而隐藏攻击来源、绕过访问控制或发起匿名攻击。该漏洞影响 WinGate 全系列早期版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0291"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.093","remediation":"立即为 WinGate 代理服务设置管理密码并启用用户认证机制；在 GateKeeper 管理控制台中配置访问控制列表，仅允许受信任的内部 IP 地址段使用代理服务；如业务不需要代理功能，直接卸载或禁用 WinGate 服务；同时在网络防火墙层面拦截外部对 8080/1080 等常见代理端口的入站连接作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0291","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0291.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0291","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0291.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/wingate.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0485.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0583","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0583.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0351","title":"多厂商 FTP 服务器 PASV 模式拒绝服务与未授权数据访问漏洞","description":"FTP 协议 PASV 被动模式存在设计缺陷，远程攻击者可利用竞争条件在合法客户端之前连接至服务器为该客户端开放的临时数据端口，导致未经授权的数据访问和敏感信息窃取。若攻击者抢先占用该数据端口，还可导致合法客户端无法完成数据传输，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多种 FTP 服务器实现，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0351"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.610","remediation":"升级至支持 PASV 地址绑定检查的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd 3.0+、ProFTPD 1.3.5+），配置数据端口仅接受与控制连接相同 IP 的连接请求。启用 FTPS（FTP over TLS/SSL，RFC 2228）加密数据通道防止窃听；条件允许时切换到 SFTP/SCP。在服务器上限制 PASV 端口范围为固定区间，并通过防火墙仅允许预期客户端 IP 访问该端口段作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://attrition.org/security/advisory/misc/infowar/iw_sec_01.txt","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3389","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0351","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0351.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8xwf-5pv7-g2w4/GHSA-8xwf-5pv7-g2w4.json","https://github.com/CWE-CAPEC/REST-API-wg/blob/5a8974308ef38e8ee4979e4a29b3b3a22c647822/json_repo/W/421.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82479/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_100_200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000509.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0583.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0590","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0590.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0358","title":"Digital Unix 4.0 MH inc 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Digital Unix 4.0 操作系统的 mh（消息处理）套件中的 inc 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地或远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的邮件消息触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而造成程序崩溃或执行任意代码，获取系统控制权限。该漏洞影响 Digital Unix 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0358"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.480","remediation":"立即从 Compaq（现 HP）获取并安装 Digital Unix 4.0 的安全补丁（补丁编号请查阅 CIAC 公告 J-027），或升级至 Tru64 UNIX 5.0 及以上版本。若无法立即打补丁，可移除 inc 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/inc）作为临时缓解措施，限制本地普通用户以 root 权限执行 inc 命令。建议改用 mailx 或 Mutt 替代 mh 套件处理本地邮件，降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-027.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12121"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0590.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0613","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0613.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0373","title":"Debian GNU/Linux Super 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 及多个类 Unix 系统中自带的 Super 工具存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。该程序以 setuid root 权限运行，用于授权普通用户以 root 身份执行特定命令。攻击者通过向 Super 提交超长的命令行参数触发缓冲区溢出，可覆盖返回地址并劫持控制流，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。由于攻击者需要本地系统访问权限，该漏洞影响范围局限于多用户环境，但一旦利用成功即实现完全提权。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0373"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.430","remediation":"升级 Debian GNU/Linux 上的 super 软件包至版本 3.12 及以上，该版本已修复缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，立即执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/super` 移除 suid 权限位以阻止提权利用，并考虑使用 sudo 替代 super 进行权限委派。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0373"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0613.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0644","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0644.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0403","title":"Cyrix CPU on Linux 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux 系统中 Cyrix CPU 存在硬件设计缺陷，本地攻击者可通过执行特定指令序列触发处理器异常，导致系统崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响使用 Cyrix 处理器的 Linux 系统，攻击者需拥有本地用户权限才能利用，无法远程触发。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0403"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.373","remediation":"建议升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.x 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续内核更新中修复。如无法升级，可通过禁用 Cyrix CPU 特定优化功能或限制本地用户访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91821080015725&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0644.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0714","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0714.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0459","title":"Linux Alpha MILO 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Alpha Linux 系统中存在本地拒绝服务漏洞。本地攻击者可通过 MILO 引导加载程序强制系统重新启动，导致系统服务不可用。该漏洞影响运行 Alpha Linux 的 DEC Alpha 架构系统，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，无需高权限即可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0459"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.440","remediation":"建议升级 MILO 引导程序至最新版本，并限制系统本地用户的登录访问权限。在生产环境中应禁用不必要的本地用户账号，并通过 `/etc/security/access.conf` 或 PAM 模块限制控制台访问。对于 Alpha 架构系统，可考虑迁移至更新的 Linux 内核版本以规避该引导层问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0459"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0714.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0591","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0591.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0360","title":"Microsoft Site Server 2.0 任意文件上传漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 2.0 与 IIS 4.0 存在任意文件上传漏洞，由于服务器未对上传文件类型进行有效过滤，远程攻击者可通过向目标网站上传包含恶意 ASP 脚本的文件，从而在服务器上远程执行任意命令。该漏洞影响部署了 IIS 4.0 的 Microsoft Site Server 2.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0360"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.747","remediation":"建议立即删除 /scripts 目录下的 cpshost.dll、uploadn.asp、uploadx.asp、upload.asp、repost.asp、postinfo.asp 等文件；如无需 Site Server 功能应直接卸载该组件。通过 IIS MMC 管理控制台检查并移除 Web 目录的 Write 写权限。使用 NTFS 文件权限确保匿名 Internet 账户 (IUSR_MACHINE) 对文件系统没有任何写入权限。鉴于该产品已停止支持，建议升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本及 IIS。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91763097004101&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20305","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0360.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0360","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0360.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0360.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jrg6-c727-f24w/GHSA-jrg6-c727-f24w.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0360.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/iis_repost_asp.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0591.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0717","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0717.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0461","title":"Linux/Unix rpcbind 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Linux、IRIX 及 Wietse Venema 实现的 rpcbind（RPC 端口映射服务）存在认证缺陷，远程攻击者无需任何身份验证即可向目标系统发送伪造源地址的 RPC 请求，从而在 rpcbind 中插入或删除服务条目，导致服务注册信息被篡改，可能进一步用于中间人攻击或劫持 RPC 调用。该漏洞影响多个 Unix 类系统的 rpcbind 组件，CVSS v2 评分 10.0，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0461"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.697","remediation":"立即升级 rpcbind 软件包至最新版本（Linux 发行版如 Red Hat 可使用 `yum update rpcbind`，Debian/Ubuntu 使用 `apt upgrade rpcbind`）。同时配置 iptables 防火墙规则仅允许信任 IP 访问 UDP/TCP 111 端口，或在 `/etc/hosts.allow` 中添加 `portmap: 信任网段`、`/etc/hosts.deny` 中添加 `portmap: ALL` 限制来源。如无需使用 NFS/RPC 服务，建议直接关闭 rpcbind 服务（`systemctl disable rpcbind && systemctl stop rpcbind`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0461"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0717.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0571","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0571.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0348","title":"Microsoft IIS ASP 缓存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Information Server (IIS) 的 ASP 缓存机制存在信息泄露漏洞。当两个虚拟服务器共享同一物理目录时，ASP 脚本缓存未能正确隔离不同虚拟服务器之间的数据，导致攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制请求，获取同一物理目录下其他虚拟站点的敏感信息。该漏洞影响多个 IIS 版本，公开利用难度较低，可能导致网站配置文件、源代码等敏感数据泄露，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0348"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.237","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft KB Q197003 安全更新（包含于 Windows NT 4.0 Security Rollup Package），该更新修复了 ASP 脚本缓存在虚拟服务器间的隔离问题。如无法安装补丁，应将每个虚拟服务器配置为使用独立的物理目录，避免不同虚拟主机共用同一目录；也可在 IIS 管理控制台中禁用 ASP 脚本文件缓存作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ197003","http://www.osvdb.org/930","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0348","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0348.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q6hg-qxrw-r3f8/GHSA-q6hg-qxrw-r3f8.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0348.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0571.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0573","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0573.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0349","title":"Microsoft IIS FTP LIST 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 的 FTP 服务中的 list (ls) 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的 FTP 列表请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响早期版本的 IIS，攻击条件低，危害严重，建议及时安装安全补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0349"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.357","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-003 提供的补丁（Q223783），或升级至 IIS 5.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中禁用 FTP 服务（停止 MSFTPSVC 服务），或限制匿名用户对 FTP 根目录的写入权限以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ188348","http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/IIS%20Remote%20FTP%20Exploit/DoS%20Attack.html","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-003","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0349","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0349.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hcx3-7fvg-jr7j/GHSA-hcx3-7fvg-jr7j.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c6867